lalr.scm -- a fast LALR parser generator for Scheme.

The distribution contains the following files:

	. README : this file.

	. lalr.scm : The parser generator. 

	. lr-dvr.scm : The LR(0) driver for the generated parsers.

It has been successfully tested under the following Scheme systems:

	- Gambit v2.2 
	- Scm 4d3 under DEC Alpha, SUN OS, Linux
	- MIT-Scheme 7.2.0 (microcode 11.127, runtime 14.160)
	- Bigloo 1.6

and it should run on any Scheme implementation that provides macros
and bitwise operations. 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION:

Just remove the quote in front of the section corresponding to your
Scheme system (in file lalr.scm).


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
